{"tid":161641,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測) 生死時速  \t奪命高校","createTime":"2017-03-18T16:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T17:13:37.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1ab8124188aeaafdaa78693b077c4cf198f7196","tid":161641,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:30:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0dbebfa9\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=9b81f230\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c5/Speedposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc5%2FSpeedposter.jpg&h=5581070f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/79/The_Faculty_movie_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F79%2FThe_Faculty_movie_poster.jpg&h=1e488bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.下班時間，在洛杉磯一棟大樓的上班族，準備搭乘電梯回家，卻不知大樓電梯已被一名炸彈客裝置炸彈，炸彈客打算利用困在電梯的人質達成目的，但是洛杉磯警察局特殊武器戰術小組警員傑克&middot;崔文（Cst. Jack Traven，基努&middot;李維飾演）發揮智慧與勇氣，破壞了炸彈客的計畫，成功救出了人質。崔文試圖進一步逮住炸彈客，但炸彈客終究還是逃之夭夭<br />\n<br />\n2.一群令學校頭痛不已的問題學生，在一次偶然的機會下，發現有一種不明的生物體出現在校園中，他們拿去做化驗時，發現那是非常奇怪的物種，同時遇水就會產生旺盛的活動力，並且會不斷的分化。<br />\n接著校園中不斷地出現怪事，老師們的行徑都跟以往大不相同，最後他們發現許多老師和所謂的乖乖牌學生都被異形寄身。這樣的理論當然被其他的人嗤之以鼻，他們只好自己去求證，同時這群學生也必須躲避異形老師的追殺..<br />\n<br />\n12 25AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0498372719fca27638ab80626e518f6a9e5190a3","tid":161641,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}